1
00:00:04,509 --> 00:00:10,113
Once Raivata Mahārāj 
went to see Brahmā in Brahmaloka.

2
00:00:10,113 --> 00:00:14,503
He needed to get a suitable husband 
for his daughter, Revatī.

3
00:00:14,793 --> 00:00:17,013
[Husband for a Six‒Meter Daughter]

4
00:00:17,474 --> 00:00:22,855
At the time two singers-dancers 
were playing named Haha and Huhu.

5
00:00:22,955 --> 00:00:29,335
So, when they finished, a couple
hundred of thousand years went by.

6
00:00:29,335 --> 00:00:33,128
It’s Brahmaloka.
Jet lag. Time zone. 
 

7
00:00:33,128 --> 00:00:36,128
It’s got more time zones 
than Russia.

8
00:00:36,128 --> 00:00:37,995
So, all of this time 
went by,

9
00:00:37,995 --> 00:00:40,052
and then Brahmā says, 
“How can I help you?”

10
00:00:40,052 --> 00:00:44,683
and he said, 
“Well, I was looking for a suitable ...

11
00:00:45,443 --> 00:00:49,693
husband for my daughter,

12
00:00:49,723 --> 00:00:58,010
but she’s in the Tretā-yuga, 
and now it’s Dvāpara-yuga,

13
00:00:58,010 --> 00:01:02,720
and she’s 17 feet tall.”

14
00:01:03,455 --> 00:01:07,793
You understand? 
She’s like, what is that?

15
00:01:07,823 --> 00:01:10,533
It’s almost 6 meters.

16
00:01:11,459 --> 00:01:14,459
She’s 6 meters tall

17
00:01:14,464 --> 00:01:20,345
because that is 
the average height of a girl,

18
00:01:20,345 --> 00:01:26,555
kṣatriya-type girl
in Tretā-yuga.

19
00:01:26,555 --> 00:01:32,225
Brahmā is like, “Hmmm, 
let me think for a minute, son.”

20
00:01:34,528 --> 00:01:41,106
He came up with Balarāma, 
“Is the perfect,

21
00:01:41,106 --> 00:01:45,294
is the only person
who can be her husband.”

22
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:50,480
But Balarāma is around 15 feet tall,
like 5 meters.

23
00:01:50,481 --> 00:01:53,791
So then they meet,
and he just kind of …

24
00:01:53,988 --> 00:01:56,315
He can do that, 
he’s Baladev.

25
00:01:56,315 --> 00:02:01,575
A little gravity 
flow thing going …

26
00:02:01,593 --> 00:02:06,624
Made her 
appropriately sized.

27
00:02:06,624 --> 00:02:07,934
[Laughing]

28
00:02:07,934 --> 00:02:09,044
And she is happy.

